title: United Kingdom 3 Year Note Yield
description: UK 3 Year Bond Yield was 3.14 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 3 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 5.59 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 3Y.
